	<li id="comment-20542">
	<p>Anna (2/17/09 @ 11:19PM) &#8211; It&#039;s very easy to do what you&#039;re asking. When you&#039;re in FB, look in the lower right corner of your screen.  You will see a little person icon with a green dot next to it.  Left click this icon, then click &quot;go offline&quot;.  You will now see a red dot instead of green, and this means you will appear as offline to all your friends whenever you are on FB.</p>
	<p><cite>Comment by Ursula &#8212; February 17, 2009 @ <a href="#comment-20542">10:58 pm</a></cite> </p>
