<p>Your account has been reactivated. Please significantly slow down the rate at which you browse Facebook, or your account may be disabled again. We would recommend that you discontinue the use of the Snap2Face application as it appears to be flagging your account as abusive. Please notify the developers of this application that this problem has occurred. We apologize for any inconvenience this has caused.</p>
<p>Basically, Snap2Face works great, just don&#039;t configure it for 5 minute updates or they will think you&#039;re a spammer.</p>
