	<p>dreamluverz, facebook removed that slider when they updated the site earlier this spring.  Your only choices on the news feed (home) page now are to move your cursor over to the right and then to hide a specific person or to hide the application (e.g., quiz or game) that they just used.  You can&#039;t opt for &quot;show less,&quot; either.  It&#039;s either all visible or all seen for the person/app &#8212; and it stinks!</p>
