	<li id="comment-46112">
	<p>Just another tip for #7. When you add an application, mouse over your &#8216;settings&#8217; and scroll down to the bottom where you will see &#8216;application settings&#8217; There will usually be 2 tabs, &#8216;bookmark&#8217; and &#8216;additional permissions&#8217;. Select the latter and uncheck the box for &#8216;Publish recent activity (one line stories) to my Wall&#8217;. I do this immediately after adding any application.</p>
	<p><cite>Comment by <a href='http://www.facebook.com/people/Jenny-Hogg/1595700081' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Jenny Hogg</a> &#8212; November 17, 2009 @ <a href="#comment-46112">10:34 am</a></cite> </p>
