	<li id="comment-46326">
	<p>any idea how to be &#039;invisible&#039; to other members while you are online working/playing on facebook?</p>
	<p><cite>Comment by <a href='http://facebook' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Shyrl</a> &#8212; November 19, 2009 @ <a href="#comment-46326">5:00 pm</a></cite> </p>
