<p>If a user had not logged in for months they may have found that private information has been made public without their consent the entire time. They will not have seen the big banner or privacy settings wizard until now, but the settings were already changed.</p>
<p>They changed my privacy setting without my permission!. </p>
<p>I consider this a violation of my privacy.</p>
