	<p>Very informative page.  I&#039;d already figured out some of this stuff but its good to have it all listed in one place.</p>
<p>Incidentally, the way to hide friends has changed &#8211; you have to edit your friends box itself (by clicking on the pencil in the top right corner of the box) and uncheck the option that says &quot;Show friend list to everyone&quot;.</p>
<p>This hides it from people that you&#039;re not friends with.  But there is no way to hide your friends list from actual friends, though.</p>
