	<li id="comment-61129">
	<p>I figured out how to do #10 since the changes. When you&#8217;re logged in, click on your profile (NOT the account settings or privacy settings, just basic profile view). You should see your wall and on the left, the box with your friends. There should be a little pencil picture showing that you can edit it. Click on it and uncheck the &#8220;Show Friends to Everyone&#8221; box. Voila!</p>
	<p><cite>Comment by Liz &#8212; March 23, 2010 @ <a href="#comment-61129">10:17 am</a></cite> </p>
