	<li id="comment-65353">
	<p>@FEDUPwFB April 29th, 2010 at 1:33 pm</p>
<p>You DO realize FB removed our control to display or not our friendships, right?</p>
<p>Facebook quietly restored the settings to hide your friends&#8230;</p>
<p>Go to:</p>
<p>- Account</p>
<p>- Privacy Settings</p>
<p>- Friends, tabs and connections</p>
<p>For &#039;Friends&#039; you have three choices: Everyone, Friends of Friends, Friends or Custom</p>
<p>To hide all your friends select &quot;custom&quot; and then in &quot;Make this visible to&quot; &quot;These People&quot; select &quot;Only me&quot;</p>
	<p><cite>Comment by <a href='http://facebookprivacyissues.blogspot.com/' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Rolo</a> &#8212; May 5, 2010 @ <a href="#comment-65353">5:36 pm</a></cite> </p>
	</li>

